# Component Reference

Autogenerated reference for every shipped component, grouped by skin
(Daisy and Suite) then by family. Regenerate with `bin/generate-docs`.

- **Daisy skin** (`Decor::Daisy::*`) — daisyUI semantic styling, generally suited to admin / internal UI.
- **Suite skin** (`Decor::Suite::*`) — bespoke design tokens (numbered shades, hairlines, custom radii + typography), suited to customer-facing UI that wants a distinct identity.
- **Skinless** (`Decor::Icon`) — single class used by both skins.

Both skins share an abstract base under `Decor::Components::*` that owns the prop API; the props listed below are each concrete component's own additions on top of the inherited shared props (`size`, `color`, `style`) and the Vident base props.

